tworks. - Power Management: New adaptive sleep policy reduces background wakeups by 8–12% during low activity.  Known Issues - Intermittent NFC timeouts under high EMI; fix scheduled for v1.2.1. - A s
ed for v1.2.1. - A subset of units manufactured in March may report battery health inconsistently due to an ADC calibration offset; see Support Article SUP-1242.  Upgrade Guidance - Devices on v1.0 or
- Devices on v1.0 or earlier should perform a two-step upgrade (v1.0 → v1.1 → v1.2) to ensure bootloader compatibility. - For fleets using A2 barcode accessories, verify accessory firmware ≥ v3.4 to m
firmware ≥ v3.4 to maintain full feature parity.
